{
  "text": "The basic idea in active contours models or snakes is to evolve a curve, subject to constraints from a given image in order to detect objects in that image [CITATION_1] . Let \u03a3 be a bounded open subset of R 2 . The algorithm is driven by optimization procedure of energy term:",
